Package: aisdk.bioc
Title: Bioconductor Semantic Extensions for aisdk
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Yonghe", "Xia", , "xiayh17@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Bioconductor-oriented semantic adapters and workflow hints for
    aisdk. This package extends the aisdk runtime with structured semantics
    for classes such as SummarizedExperiment, SingleCellExperiment,
    DESeqDataSet, DelayedArray, HDF5Array, and GRanges without making
    the core package own domain-specific object logic.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: aisdk, methods, rlang
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0), knitr, rmarkdown, SummarizedExperiment,
    SingleCellExperiment, GenomicRanges, IRanges, S4Vectors, DESeq2,
    DelayedArray, HDF5Array
Config/testthat/edition: 3
